headline: Moody’s Acquires Numerated Growth Technologies, Expanding Lending Technology Solutions
summary: NEW YORK, November 21, 2024--Moody’s Corporation (NYSE:MCO) announced today that it has acquired Numerated Growth Technologies (Numerated), a loan origination platform for financial institutions. The transaction further expands Moody’s Lending Suite capabilities across the credit lifecycle, providing banking customers with a powerful end-to-end loan origination and monitoring solution.
